trans-unit.source: Provides a thread-safe list of <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 스레드로부터 안전한 <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener" /> 개체 목록을 제공합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection> list is used to specify the output listeners for the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> and the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> collections.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection> 목록은 됩니다에 대 한 출력 수신기를 지정 하는 데는 <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 및 <xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: You cannot create an instance of this class.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스의 인스턴스를 만들 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: This list is thread-safe, however the methods used to access the list and the enumerator do not take synchronization locks.
trans-unit.target: 이 목록은 스레드로부터 안전한 목록 및 열거자에 액세스 하는 데 사용 하는 메서드 동기화 잠금을 수행 하지 않습니다.

trans-unit.source: Instead, the collection is copied, the copy is modified, and a reference is set to the copy of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 대신, 컬렉션을 복사 하 고 복사본을 수정 고 컬렉션의 복사본에 대 한 참조 설정 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Methods like <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Add%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Remove%2A>, and <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Clear%2A> modify the elements in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 와 같은 메서드 <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Add%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Remove%2A>, 및 <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Clear%2A> 컬렉션의 요소를 수정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection> class provides the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Count%2A> property for information about the list.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection> 클래스를 제공는 <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Count%2A> 속성 목록에 대 한 정보에 대 한 합니다.

trans-unit.source: It also provides the following methods: <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Contains%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.GetEnumerator%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.IndexOf%2A>.

This class also provides the following methods to modify the list: <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Add%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Clear%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Insert%2A>, and <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Remove%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스는 또한 목록을 수정 하려면 다음 방법 제공: <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Add%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Clear%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Insert%2A>, 및 <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Remove%2A>합니다.

trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.CopyTo%2A> 메서드 목록의 일부를 배열에 복사 합니다.
